main event: A report was made of a red object hovering over Sem City at an altitude of about 2,000 feet on March 25, 1966.
interesting points: The incident involved multiple sightings reported through the command post., The patrol car reported the sighting at 2200 hrs., March AFB aircraft were dispatched to investigate but returned negative reports., The physical evidence was lacking or reported as insufficient., The witness name remains unknown.
sighted object: a red object hovering in the sky
witness description: unknown witness based on the patrol car report
